=== Annual festival ===
At the annual grand festival held on May 3, dedicatory performances include the Urayasu dance, daimyo procession, lion dance, mikoshi procession, and hemp-plain sacred boat. Among these, the {{ill|lt=lion dance|Q713866|WD=Q713866|1=Lion dance}} is designated an {{ill|lt=Ehime Prefecture|Q123376|WD=Q123376|1=Ehime Prefecture}} intangible folk cultural property, and the mikoshi procession is designated an {{ill|lt=Imabari|Q461020|WD=Q461020|1=Imabari, Ehime}} intangible folk cultural property.

